    <title>博客搭建教程16 - 知识财产保护</title>
    <url>/2023/01/09/bo-ke-da-jian-jiao-cheng-16-zhi-shi-cai-chan-bao-hu/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>本篇介绍以下内容<br>其它站点引用协议<br>转载协议<br>图片水印<br>盗链与防盗链<br>简单的防盗链设置<br><a href="https://www.huati365.com/16b0661323e8cec6">https://www.huati365.com/16b0661323e8cec6</a><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_52162404/article/details/127051356">https://blog.csdn.net/qq_52162404/article/details/127051356</a><br><a href="https://www.jb51.net/article/251177.htm">https://www.jb51.net/article/251177.htm</a></p>
<p>总结下来写法<br>修改&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;conf&#x2F;nginx.conf文件，<br>如果这个是注释的状态，则将其打开</p>
<p><img src="/images/pasted-18.png" class="lazyload placeholder" data-srcset="/images/pasted-18.png" srcset="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-cd38920285d125be80b3eb504052c550_b.webp" alt="upload successful"><br>增加下面代码</p>
<p><img src="/images/pasted-20.png" class="lazyload placeholder" data-srcset="/images/pasted-20.png" srcset="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-cd38920285d125be80b3eb504052c550_b.webp" alt="upload successful"></p>
<p>然后nginx -s reload<br>如果自己的网站能显示图片，其它网站CNAME过来的就不显示图片<br>如果检测到盗链行为则用一张图片回击，其它盗链网站效果如下<br><img src="/images/pasted-12.png" class="lazyload placeholder" data-srcset="/images/pasted-12.png" srcset="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-cd38920285d125be80b3eb504052c550_b.webp" alt="upload successful"><br>也可以使用七牛云等专业图床，可以设置防盗链，但是需要服务器有备案<br>无版权素材<br>常见侵权行为</p>
]]></content>
